comment: I did not have a great brew day for Tastys APA. Such a shame too, I had such high hopes for this crowd pleaser... Got terrible efficiency, botched my strike temp, mashed hella high (157) for 30mins & missed my volumes. Made up for the crappy eff by adding 6oz dme. Still managed to end up at 1.057 OG, but only time will tell we're this'll end up with the high mash temp
